the whole meeting was the initial meeting of a new remote control project .
firstly , project manager introduced the scope and agenda of the project , and the team got acquainted with each other and technical devices .
then project manager made clear that remote control would be priced at 25 euros and a production cost of 12.5 euros , in order to achieve a profit aim of 50 million euros .
after an accident , marketing suggested that remote control should be made multipurpose and the consensus was reached on this point .
finally , the group brainstormed some other functions for the remote control despite a potential increase in production cost .
